sellerCard.oneLiner: Shopify dropshipping and ecommerce development expert
sellerCard.description: Hello, My name is Abdul Basit. I have been into Ecommerce development since 2017 and made 1000+ Ecommerce stores. Specifically, I started Shopify Dropshipping in its early days around 2018. In last 3 years, I have successfully created 100s of profitable stores. Currently, I am creating shopify stores and wordpress stores for walmart approval or amazon FBA wholesale brand approval.

description.content:
Hello!


Thank you for considering my services!


I'm Abdul Basit, a full-stack developer with 6 years of hands-on experience in crafting dynamic and responsive websites. I specialize in creating tailored web solutions for individuals, small businesses, and corporate clients.


If you're looking to design or revamp a sleek, modern website that works flawlessly across mobile, desktop, and laptop screens, you're in the right place!

Here's what I can do to bring your vision to life:


Programming Languages:

  • PHP
  • Javascript


Front-end Development:

  • React .js
  • CSS/SCSS
  • HTML
  • JavaScript
  • Jquery


Ô∏èBackend Development:

  • PHP - Laravel MVC
  • Databases - MYSQL, MongoDB, NoSQL, Firebase
  • Client/server, database/web interfaces


Variety of style packages:

  • Tailwind CSS
  • Material-UI
  • Styled-components
  • Framer Motion


Ready to move forward? Contact me to discuss your project requirements and get a customized quote.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is your experience in Website development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For the past 6 years, I've worked as a full-stack web developer.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be Responsive with mobile devices?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, all of the websites I create are fully responsive and mobile friendly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you convert Figma to HTML?
Do you offer any assistance after the site is launched?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide 30-day free assistance, however you can contact me after one month. I am always available to assist you with your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be allowed to make future changes to the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you may easily change your website in the future, and I will also guide you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What services are included in this gig?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: - UI/UX design - Frontend development - Backend development - Database integration - API development and integration - Testing and debugging - Deployment and maintenance
